\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Blur the line between clean and unclean}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Consume human flesh.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Have sex with dead girl.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Things outside of society.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Push you beyond the idea of good/bad/ugly/beautiful}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 When they find temselves near death aghoris deliberately leave their bodies and enter the bodies of corpses, taking them over and making them live for as long as they please, until they decide to change bodies again.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Most dead personalities cannot move about so freely on their own, and some tantrics worship in graveyards and charnelgrounds simply to catch hold of human spirits and force them to perform work. THe most puissant are deities, personifications of cosmic forces. The ultimate siddhi is control of adya, the personification of the entire cosmos.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Essential to the production of any siddhi are mantr, yantra, and tantra. Mantra is the energy which moves your vehicle (the yantra) according to the road map (tantra). }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 A true tantric regards every human being as already dead since the fact of birth makes death inevitable. The entire world is a playground and a temple.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 On this path the chances for catastropohe are great unless a powerful guru\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s protection is provided. The sexual rituals which have made tantra notorious are part of vama marge.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Panch amakara.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Sattvic people naturally enjoy ample sattva (balance of mind and alertness) and do not require external aids to worship. They utilize the meat of silence, the fish of breath control, the grain of concentration techniques the wine of god intoxication, and the coitus of one\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s ego with the absoluute.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 There is no freedom from delusion without enjoyment - enjoyment refers to the acceptance of all phenomena which may occur to an individual, be they \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91good\u8217\'92 or \u8216\'91bad\u8217\'92. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Such self-delusive activity reinforces the crystallizations of the personality which prevent spiritual progress.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Ordinary sex is no sacrifice. When two people come together to copulate they usually seek gratification for themselves, the slaking of their lust. Perhaps indirectly they will try to satisfy their partners. Tantric sex becomes possible only when one has totally effaced one\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s own personality and offers oneself for the gratification of the deity, the universe incarnate.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 This is one reason tantra has always been a closely guarded secret. The danger of abusable knowledge falling into the hands of the unworthy has limited its spread. One should never seek to practice classical tantr without a guru because no tantric texts exist which provide thoroughly accurate details of any ritual. Each text omits an essential step, or includes false information, and only through a guru can the reality, handed down through generations, be known.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Unfortunately even the tantric attitude can be dangerous. As one accumulates power, the ego will balloon out unless the personality is continuously incinerated simultaneously. Hence Tantra\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s insistence that power be objectified and personified.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 All males should learn motherly love. Motherliness. Worship of mother; a method for inculcating maternal feelings.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Tantra has thus far been glimpsed in the west only in its most vulgar and debased forms, promulgated by unscrupulous scoundrels who equate sex with superconsciousness. Sex is indeed central to tantra, the cosmic sexual union of universal dualities. The aim of tantra is laya, return of the seeker to the state of undifferentiated existence.  It consists only of methods ofr achieving this Laya, or union of the individual with the infinite. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The Left-hand path has attracted attention to itself by the actions of those unwise souls who seek quick and easy spiritual development without any preliminary renunciation of sensory gratification. The result of suhc rashness is invariably indulgence of the worst and most blatant sort.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Most serious practitioners shun the left hand path because of its potential for misuse, which is great. It is truly treacherous for the unwary: walking on swords or riding a tiger is child\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s play by comparison.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aghora is not indulgence; it is the forcible transformation of darkness into light. Renunciation disappears once you arrive at the absolute because then nothing remains to renounce. An aghori goes so deeply into the darkness, into all things undreamable to ordinary mortals, that he comes out into light. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 Popularly, aghoris have been stereotyped as ash-swathed ascetics with long matted hair who walk through life wild-eyed, skulking about in charnel grounds, wrestling with jackals for carcasses. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 To vimalananda, the true aghori cannot be recognized by any external sign or mark. Experience in the world of ascetics had taught him that many fake aghoris lurk under outward appurtenances. The true aghora is wholly internal. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 To his spiritual children he was the perfect mother - to those with inflated spiritual egos he was merciless.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Death is to be personified and deified. They crave not physical death, but for destruction of all their limitations, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91killing\u8217\'92 themselves by internal or external processes. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91Filth and orgies in the graveyard\u8217\'92 can be as conducive to spiritual advancement as can asanas, pranayama, and other purer disciplines.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aghora is mysterious and deep - deeper than deep, in fact - and only those who can lay aside all their cultural clothing and plunge into it naked can dive into it\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s depths.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He wanted to warn spiritual dilettantes in the west that the frivolity with which they treat discipline and the self-delusion they attempt to pass fof as enlightenment is merely a cheating of their own consciousness whcih leads only to the pit.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Has the kundalini shakti become so cheap that some so-called godman can awaken it in multitudes of people all at once? NO! Were our Rishis (ancient seers) fools to spend decades out in the jungles working hard at penances to waken kundalini and to perfect aghora? No, the people who think they can buy kundalini are fools. Westerners think they can purchase knowledge, but all they get for their money is fake teachers from india who dish out any slop to them and get rich on their gullibility.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Most people who know him only formally never suspected that he might be ofa spiritual bent. He cultivated this carefree image deliberately to avoid attracting attention to himself. Ate meat on occasion, intoxicants, smoked cigarettes incessantly.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He made a show of complete disinterest in teachign while actually spending much time evaluating the strenghts and weaknesses of each of his spiritual \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93children\u8221\'94. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Tortoise teacher - pay no attention to progress, but in reality monitors them closely, like a tortoise burying eggs in sand.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 When he decided I should learn something he would deftly insert it into a flood of mundane trivialities directed at others in the room and would expect me to be alert enough to pick it out. Weeks or months later he would question me about it, without warning. - what use is an exam if you\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92re warned about it ahead of time.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Me-when you are with a lover you are a different person. Why not be that person to all people, all the time?}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 His impression on people was achieved primarily not by what he did, but by how he did it; not by what he said, but by how he said it. Who he was was more significant than what he did, but he made people dig for his interior reality and most often they would come up empty-handed.  Those few who knew him well - at least superficially - could never agree with each other on who he was, because his personality differed for each of his friends. He was a multitude of different people, all in one body.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 His foster daughter had the last word, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No one has any business to read about you because unless they have experienced you they could never know the reality.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Spoke mainly for indians, who often inflate the content of events they report. Indian listeners have learned to automatically compensate for this expansion by mentally scaling down whateveris said.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Ability to change eye color at will.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Even if the child is wicked or wayward, do the parents stop loving it? No! In fact, if they are true parents they will love the child all the more, because that child gives them the opportunity to demonstrate their generosity and love, just as in the case of the prodigal son. It is an opportunity to feed the ego.}
